            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"pattern-0-baseline-no-protection\">Pattern 0: Baseline (No Protection)</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Shows the vulnerability: untrusted content is passed directly to an LLM with tools.\nThe injection in the email body will likely cause the LLM to follow malicious instructions.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>This is how most production systems work today.</strong></span></span>"
